			<p>Many patients prefer home consultations, but most doctors don’t have a structured way to offer them.</p>
			<p><b>Our goal is to bridge this gap.</b></p>	
			<p>We aim to do this by ensuring doctors get access to these patients <b>without losing their professional value</b>.</p>	
			<p><b>You treat patients. We take care of the rest.</b></p>	
			<p>We believe in <b>long-term partnerships</b> with doctors—our exclusive early members get priority for future opportunities, including ESOPs</p>	
			<p><b>Don’t miss this opportunity. Join early and unlock more benefits!</b></p>	
			<p></p>	
		</div>
